V0702_01_00_00_0.text:
I'm the top Duelist at Goha 7!
No one's taking me down!

V0702_01_00_01_0.text: If you wanna know the secret to my strength, I'll show ya!

V0702_01_00_02_0.text:
Of course you wanna Duel me.
If I could, I'd Duel me too!

V0702_01_00_03_0.text: You think you stand a chance against the next King of Duels?

V0702_01_00_04_0.text: There's a lot more to Rush Duels than you know, bro!

V0702_01_00_05_0.text: If you're a Duelist, then we gotta Duel, bro!

V0702_01_00_06_0.text: Every Duel brings me closer to the throne!

V0702_01_00_07_0.text:
You're gonna Duel me!
You're so gonna Duel me!

V0702_01_00_08_0.text: As your future King, I promise I won't let you down, Yuga!

V0702_01_00_09_0.text:
Yuga!
I gotta defeat you if I wanna be the King of Duels!

V0702_01_00_10_0.text:
Want me to teach ya how to Rush Duel?
...Hey! Come back!

V0702_01_00_11_0.text:
Romin!
You traitoring again, you traitorous traitor!?

V0702_01_00_12_0.text:
Gavin!
If I win, I get to be student council president!

V0702_01_00_14_0.text:
Let's go, Tiadosia!
You don't scare me!
...Maybe a little.

V0702_03_00_00_0.text:
Your strategy's fizzled out!
You're going down!

V0702_03_00_01_0.text: I can see the future - and it ends with my win!

V0702_03_00_05_0.text: You shoulda finished me when you had the chance, bro!

V0702_05_00_00_0.text: With this draw, I'm on the highway to victory!

V0702_07_09_01_0.text: I'll use the card I Set!

V0702_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0702_16_00_01_0.text: Time to turn out the lights!

V0702_21_00_03_0.text: I got plenty 'a tricks saved for later.

V0702_21_00_05_1.text:
Heh.
Don't forget I have powers beyond those of mortal men.

V0702_28_00_00_0.text:
Don't be sad, bro.
You were facing the future King!

V0702_28_00_01_0.text:
I'm one step closer to the crown!
Hahahaha!

V0702_28_00_02_0.text: My highway leads to the throne!

V0702_28_00_02_1.text: You're looking at the next King of Duels!

V0702_28_00_03_0.text: I forgot that the King's gotta show mercy to his court!

V0702_28_00_04_0.text:
All you need is skills!
And some luck - but mostly skills!

V0702_28_00_05_0.text: You gotta try harder than that to clog my highway!

V0702_28_00_06_0.text: Your monsters were scary, but not as much as my dragons.

V0702_28_00_07_0.text:
Dueling isn't about winning or losing.
But it's nice to win!

V0702_28_00_08_0.text: That was an awesome Duel, Yuga!

V0702_28_00_09_0.text: As the creator of Rush Duels, you gotta do better than that!

V0702_28_00_10_0.text:
Ya still got much to learn, Romin.
But I'm a great teacher!

V0702_28_00_11_0.text:
Since I won, I'm the new president of Goha 7!
Mwahaha!

V0702_28_00_12_0.text:
See that, Sis!
I can handle my own!

V0702_28_00_13_0.text: If you wanna be a hero to the max, stay true to yourself!

V0702_29_00_00_0.text: I can't be the King if I can't get the win...

V0702_29_00_01_0.text: This Duelist was tougher than concrete!

V0702_29_00_02_0.text:
I shoulda focused more.
My bad!

V0702_29_00_03_0.text:
You beat me...
Does that mean you're the King of Duels?

V0702_29_00_04_0.text: I'll never forget your name... for at least three days!

V0702_29_00_05_0.text: You must be a tactical tactician to defeat me, bro!

V0702_29_00_06_0.text:
I get it!
You were trying to teach me how I should Duel!

V0702_29_00_06_1.text: That's why you're my bro, bro!

V0702_29_00_07_0.text:
You want to be the King of Duels too?
That's cool!

V0702_29_00_07_1.text: Cuz when you become King, you can share the crown with me!

V0702_29_00_08_0.text:
Wow...
Every time we Duel, you have a new strategy to play!

V0702_29_00_09_0.text:
Romin!
Since when did you get so good?

V0702_29_00_10_0.text: You must study for hours to come up with these moves.

V0702_29_00_10_1.text: If that means you're too busy to be Prez, I'll take the job.

V0702_33_00_00_0.text: The King of Duels is unstoppable, bro!

V0702_33_00_01_0.text: Ride on my highway to the stars!

V0702_33_00_02_0.text: You're goin' down whether you like it or not!

V0702_33_00_03_0.text: If you believe in your cards, the cards'll believe in you!

V0702_33_00_04_0.text: The King can make miracles come true!

V0702_33_00_05_0.text: My skill is a power beyond those of mortal men!

V0702_30_00_00_0.text:
Hahaha!
That's right that's right that's right!

V0702_30_00_01_0.text: You're right - but I'm not giving up!

V0702_30_00_02_0.text: You can't fool me! That's a trap!

V0702_34_00_00_0.text: Are you flattering me or buttering me up?

V0702_34_00_01_0.text:
Let's train!
Attack! Defend! Attack! Defend!
Draw draw draw!

V0702_34_00_02_0.text: Go ahead and do your thing, bro!

V0702_34_00_03_0.text: I give that a standing ovation!

V0702_34_00_04_0.text: Two Level 4 monsters... Here it comes!

V0702_34_00_05_0.text: You won't get away with wasting my cards!

V0702_34_00_08_0.text: Even if I say I'm OK with that, I'm not OK with that!

V0702_34_00_10_0.text:
Serious!?
You better not be kidding!

V0702_34_00_11_0.text: Time to do my zap zap thing!

V0702_34_00_12_0.text:
*pant pant*
I'm all out of juice.

V0702_34_00_14_0.text: That's proof I have powers beyond those of mortal men.
